This paper discusses the connection between ordinary differential equations and deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses optimization methods and applications in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of Pontryagin's maximum principle, which is a popular method in optimal control (cs.NA) and the training of neural networks (cs.AI).
